---
title: Creamy Pulled Chicken & Corn Soup with Roast Veggies & Parmesan Crisps
description: We take off our hats for this soup. Top the tender pulled chicken and roast veggie soup with it’s own dapper hat, a
Parmesan crisp one. It’s an elegant addition to a soup of this stature. We shall leave you to your meal now, good day!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
